# Yunost, Sharansky District, Republic of Bashkortostan

}}
Yunost () is a rural locality (a village) in Michurinsky Selsoviet, Sharansky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 106 as of 2010. There are 2 streets.
Geography
Yunost is located 26&nbsp;km northeast of Sharan (the district's administrative centre) by road. Yelanchikbash is the nearest rural locality.
